high_descs: Turn around, take a left at the round table and walk to the counter on the left with the coffee maker.
Pick up the tomato to the right of the sink on the counter.
Head left and walk to the white fridge on the right.
Put the tomato inside the fridge on the shelf to the right side, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and head left to the microwave on the counter.
Put the chilled tomato inside the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the black chair then turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the sink turning left to face it when you get there.
Pick up the tomato that's in front of you.
Turn left and walk to the black chair then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Chill the tomato in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and take a large step forward then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave please.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato in the microwave.
